Basarigino (Russian: Басаргино) is a rural locality (a village) in Rostilovskoye Rural Settlement, Gryazovetsky District, Vologda Oblast, Russia. The population was 15 as of 2002.


== Geography ==
The distance to Gryazovets is 6 km, to Rostilovo is 0.3 km. Talitsa is the nearest rural locality.


